This Echo Stream client plugin allows to limit the amount of visible items in the stream when a live update reaches the client side. When new items are rendered, the old ones are removed from the visual part of the stream.

Version: 2.0 (07/18/2011)
Developed by: Echo Solutions team (Kushnir Andrew)
Documentation: http://wiki.aboutecho.com/Community-Developed-Plugins#StreamRootItemsLimiter
